@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cmwymh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.67 + 0.35) - (wp.exp(tmp + 0.17) - tmp))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.63)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.87)) + wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.27)))
    tmp = 0.21
    tmp = v1
    v0 = (0.23 - ((tmp + 0.77 / v2 + 0.88) - (tmp + 0.30 * v1 + 0.19)))
    data[tid] = v0
